<item>
            <title>[JDK-8326734] text-decoration applied to &lt;span&gt; lost when mixed with &lt;u&gt; or &lt;s&gt;</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8326734</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>The value of &amp;#39;text-decoration&amp;#39; property applied to &amp;lt;span&amp;gt; gets lost when it&amp;#39;s mixed with &amp;lt;u&amp;gt; or &amp;lt;s&amp;gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;u&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: line-through&amp;#39;&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/u&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;s&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: underline&amp;#39;&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/s&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: line-through&amp;#39;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;u&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/u&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: underline&amp;#39;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;s&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/s&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
These four snippets should produce text which renders both underline and line-through. Yet they render only the style applied to the &amp;lt;span&amp;gt; element.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Two &amp;lt;span&amp;gt; elements don&amp;#39;t work either:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: line-through&amp;#39;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: underline&amp;#39;&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: underline&amp;#39;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;span style=&amp;#39;text-decoration: line-through&amp;#39;&amp;gt;underline + line-through&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Only the latest value is respected.</description>
